texts.text: Durango is a character in the Minecraft Mini-Series and part of Team Mesa with River (Character).

Durango is referred to as a cowboy and looks the part. He has brown hair and a beard, black eyes and light skin. He wears a hat, dark blue shirt with light blue sleeves, brown pants, and light brown shoes.

Durango can be hot-headed, cocky, materialistic, and competitive especially when gold is promised. He likes to be in charge, creating plans, and eating meat. In the Challenge of the Spooky Isles he grows a rivalry with Quinn, but in the Mystery of the Greek Isles they puts their differences aside to defeat Poseidon's games.
Durango is shown to be a mesa rancher when "interviewed" in-between clips.
